== Sample app for Rails 3 / Devise / Mongoid / Oauth

A quick sample app showing how to configure rails 3, devise,
mongoid, and oauth to work together.  Don't forget to update
config/initializers/devise.rb with the correct facebook secrets.

Slides on what has been done can be found on slideshare here:

http://www.slideshare.net/sevatt/rails-3-devise-oauth2-mongoid-installation-guide
